Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.46,0:28:46.16,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H181818&}―I believe…believe in you―
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.16,0:28:50.26,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H181818&}きっと一番の約束の言葉
